<h1>
    How do they work, and how do I use them?
</h1>
<p>
    When CSS and HTML are used together, they are powerful tools used to create all web pages on the internet.  In addition, another language called JavaScript is used for many web pages.  JavaScript isn’t covered in these lessons, but lessons on JavaScript are also available on this site.  HTML is used to structure the web page and CSS is used to make the page look interesting, while JavaScript is used to add functionality.

    Look at these pictures to get a better understanding of how the three languages work together:

</p>
